Description:
About the job
Job Title: Azure AI Copilot Studio Model Trainer

Job Summary:
We're seeking an experienced AI professional to train and fine-tune AI models using Azure AI Copilot Studio. The successful candidate will work closely with our development team to build and deploy AI-powered solutions.

Key Responsibilities
Design and implement high-quality training datasets for AI models
Train and fine-tune AI models using Azure AI Copilot Studio
Collaborate with developers to integrate trained models into applications
Monitor model performance and optimize as needed
Stay up-to-date with industry trends and advancements in AI

Requirements:
1. Experience with Azure AI services, particularly Azure AI Copilot Studio
2. Strong understanding of machine learning (Azure ML) concepts and model training
3. Proficiency in Python and relevant libraries (e.g., TensorFlow, PyTorch)
4. Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail

Nice to Have:
1. Experience with cloud-based AI services
2. Knowledge of natural language processing (NLP) or computer vision
3. Familiarity with agile development methodologies
